broot
Tags: file-managers, terminal

Tree-style terminal file manager and navigator with previews and custom actions.

Important note:
broot is best launched as `br` when you want shell integration such as `cd` back into the caller.

Help head:
Usage: broot [options] [ROOT]
ROOT: Root Directory
--show-git-info   Show git statuses on files and stats on repo
--hidden          Show hidden files
--git-ignored     Show git ignored files
